{"tid":676329,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【這些機會......】齊人之福細哨享 8月娶兩個咩玩法？","createTime":"2018-05-24T09:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T10:27:18.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e40fb6d929f927252c0c7c4dabd958897370cc","tid":676329,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180524/large/1527152417_d874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F1527152417_d874.jpg&h=45190a42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴西名宿朗拿甸奴，由踢波時期到退役後一向愛蒲，身邊嘅女伴多到數唔晒，據巴西傳媒講，嚟到38歲細哨都有心成家立室，不過點知8月原來佢打算一次過娶兩位女士，分別係Priscilla Coelho同埋Beatriz Souza。<br />\n<br />\n原來自從去年12月開始，細哨已經玩緊三人行，大家一齊住喺里約熱內盧入面一間價值500萬鎊嘅細哨物業，仲生活得好和諧！細哨每次飛離巴西做嘢，兩位女友都會一齊去咁話。<br />\n其實，細哨幾年前開始同Priscilla拍拖，不過2016年就搭上埋Beatriz，一路每個月兩位女士都只係由細哨俾1,500鎊零用錢。同時細哨都夠晒公道，聽講每次買禮物都會買兩份一式一樣嘅，俾晒兩個女友，仲連香水都同一隻味，睇嚟細哨好清楚女人嘅呷醋心態。據講，舊年4月Priscilla嘅家人因為唔滿意細哨一腳踏兩船，想同佢攤牌，但係最後變埋三人行。<br />\n<br />\n呢位前世界足球先生，1月同時同兩人求婚，8月就會喺巴西里約熱內盧搞個私人典禮。根據巴西法律，婚姻都係一夫一妻制嘅，可能細哨只係搞個儀式當禮成啦，據報佢嘅家姐Deisi好反對細哨玩一夫多妻，所以唔會出席，而巴西歌手Jorge Vercillo就會做嘉賓負責唱歌。<br />\n<br />\nPriscilla同Beatriz都係出身自細哨前球會明尼路嘅根據地Belo Horizonte，今年3月細哨去日本出trip，兩位女友都喺身邊，當時細哨有拍片擺上ig。而目前係巴塞隆拿同國際足協大使嘅細哨，亦有傳想學前輩羅馬里奧咁，喺巴西參政，並且加入中間偏右嘅巴西共和黨（PRB）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/G7CoCWARhRhJe/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FG7CoCWARhRhJe%2Fgiphy.gif&h=47269d87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/de/eb/42/deeb42e7220ec63d60c281eb12249a5d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fde%2Feb%2F42%2Fdeeb42e7220ec63d60c281eb12249a5d.gif&h=7fca3205&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddeaacc63fa0e4060dd583606d7d6211b0026455","tid":676329,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6a67e7ab2ff569df8288c9e9019c6ab5f3aced","tid":676329,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"女權閪去晒邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad91223f173e54555c2eed49831235032d301ca","tid":676329,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T09:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c203120267ff285e50a32ae4f931aa90c32b7f","tid":676329,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:20:28.000Z","msg":"晚晚3p"},{"pid":"9baf00304aecebe5ab575dba63e0b145f4da4646","tid":676329,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:22:33.000Z","msg":"做細哨條女先得果1500磅零用咁撚cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎香港比個有錢佬包，十倍都唔止"},{"pid":"4ddbe3746d8a20f6bb905d2cfe45edeabb792280","tid":676329,"uid":27915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9baf00304aecebe5ab575dba63e0b145f4da4646","tid":676329,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:22:33.000Z","msg":"做細哨條女先得果1500磅零用咁撚cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎香港比個有錢佬包，十倍都唔止"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"細哨踢開波，可能下面好勁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}